                                <para>On</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3" rotate="0">
                                <para>Attempt to exercise the warning lamp with the "INTUNE" diagnostic software.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col5" rotate="0">
                                <para>Warning lamp responds to EGC diagnostic input.</para>
                            </entry>
