                                <para>Warning lamp responds to EGC diagnostic input.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col6" rotate="0">
                                <para>Lamp circuits from data link to EGC are working correctly.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col7" rotate="0">
